# Version Bump Rule

When building an APK or AAB (via `eas build` or any production build command):

1. **Always increment `android.versionCode`** in `tv-guide-app/app.json` before starting the build
2. `versionCode` must be strictly greater than the previous value — both Google Play and Amazon Appstore reject duplicate codes
3. If the changes warrant it, also bump `version` (semver string) — use patch for fixes, minor for features
